GPU runtime libraries (NVIDIA)
------------------------------
The `nvidia-cu13-*` pip wheels (CUDA 13 runtime, cuDNN 9) ship under the
NVIDIA Software Development Kit EULA, not an OSI-approved license.
Redistribution is permitted under that EULA's conditions:

  - The redistributing application must add material additional
    functionality beyond the SDK itself (GridLoraTester does).
  - Only the components listed in Attachment A of the EULA for the target
    CUDA version may be bundled.
  - The NVIDIA attribution notice must be preserved.

Reference: https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/eula/index.html

If you build a redistributable Docker image or installer from this
project, verify Attachment A coverage for the specific CUDA / cuDNN
versions you ship before distributing.

================================================================================
                  THIRD-PARTY MODELS — NOT DISTRIBUTED HEREWITH
================================================================================

GridLoraTester orchestrates third-party machine-learning models that it
downloads at runtime from external sources (Hugging Face Hub, InsightFace
release mirrors). These model weights are NOT bundled with this software
and are NOT covered by this License. Users must independently obtain
valid licenses for any model they choose to run, in addition to any
license required for GridLoraTester itself.

The following defaults referenced by the code carry non-permissive
licenses that restrict commercial use:

  FLUX.2-klein-9B (default --model-path for grid generation)
  ----------------------------------------------------------
    License: FLUX.2 Non-Commercial License (Black Forest Labs)
    Restricts:  revenue-generating activity, direct end-user interactions,
                training / fine-tuning / distillation for commercial use.
    Commercial path:  paid Self-Serve or Enterprise license from BFL.
                      https://bfl.ai/licensing
    Alternative:  FLUX.2-klein-4B is Apache-2.0 and is unrestricted for
                  commercial use. Pass
                    --model-path black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-klein-4B
                  to opt into the permissive variant.

  InsightFace `buffalo_l` model pack (default face-similarity scoring)
  -------------------------------------------------------------------
    License: Non-commercial research only (DeepInsight).
    Restricts:  any commercial use, including internal use by a commercial
                operation that processes customer data through the model.
    Commercial path:  paid commercial license from DeepInsight.
                      Contact: recognition-oss-pack@insightface.ai

A commercial license for GridLoraTester does NOT include or extend to
third-party model licenses. Commercial licensees remain solely responsible
for obtaining valid licenses for every model used at runtime.

